\(\begin{array}{ccc} $dB & \overset{R_1 \Leftrightarrow R_3}{\sim} & $dB2 \\
& \overset{\begin{align*}$p1 R_1 + R_2 &\Rightarrow R_2 \\ $p2 R_1 + R_3 &\Rightarrow R_3\end{align*}}{\sim} & $dB1 \\ & \overset{$p3 + R_3 \Rightarrow R_3}{\sim} & $dEch \end{array}\) $PAR
